data.description: Great end unit townhouse, ideally located in central Mount Pleasant. This home is an opportunity to own in Hunter's Trace subdivision at an affordable price under $350k - a rare find in today's market and also low annual Hoa fee. Two bedroom, bath and half with nice layout to maximize living space. Ample storage with fenced backyard and large concrete and stone patio. Location allows for easy commute to downtown Charleston via highway 17. Some work needed to suit and is being sold as-is, no repairs will be made by seller. Final sale is subject to court approval. Come take a look, you will be pleasantly pleased by this property.
